No longer works with the Twitter APIs gone.

RIP Twitter


tgrep - a cli tool for searching twitter 

# make sure your GOPATH is set, e.g. export GOPATH=$HOME/go
go get github.com/imarko/tgrep

$GOPATH/bin/tgrep -f '#golang' 

Usage of tgrep:
  -f, --follow=false: follow mode
  -F, --followdelay=1m0s: refresh delay in follow mode
  -n, --number=20: number of items to return
  -R, --retweets=false: include retweeets
  -r, --reverse=false: reverse order

